Package: athleteR
Title: Sports and Athletics Data Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Student", "Author", email = "student@university.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing sports and athletics performance data.
    Provides functions for computing athlete performance metrics, comparing players across
    seasons, visualizing athletic trends, and summarizing team statistics. Designed for
    sports analysts, coaches, and researchers working with structured athletic datasets.
    Includes built-in sample datasets and S3 classes for athlete and team objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
